    "attributes": {
        "action": "Introduce requirements for all stage/screen scenes with nudity/intimacy",
        "additional_details": "This is for the safety of all involved. This will help prevent actors and performers being taken advantage of. Any intimacy or nudity scenes must be included in a shared printed script given to actors in advance with another crew member present. This would help remove the power imbalance faced by actors.\r\n \r\n",
        "background": "Make it a legal requirement for production of all stage or screen intimacy or nudity scenes to have an intimacy co-ordinator present. Scenes must also be planned in writing in advance.",
